sentences.sentence_0: Federal Register, Volume 86 Issue 29 (Tuesday, February 16, 2021) [Federal Register Volume 86, Number 29 (Tuesday, February 16, 2021)] [Notices] [Page 9543] From the Federal Register Online via the Government Publishing Office [[URL] [FR Doc No: 2021-03002] ----------------------------------------------------------------------- NATIONAL ARCHIVES AND RECORDS ADMINISTRATION [NARA-2021-017] National Industrial Security Program Policy Advisory Committee (NISPPAC) Meeting AGENCY: Information Security Oversight Office (ISOO), National Archives and Records Administration (NARA).

sentences.sentence_1: ACTION: Notice of Federal Advisory Committee meeting.

sentences.sentence_2: ----------------------------------------------------------------------- SUMMARY: We are announcing an upcoming meeting of the National Industrial Security Program Policy Advisory Committee (NISPPAC).

sentences.sentence_3: DATES: The meeting will be on April 14, 2021, from 10:00 am to 1:00 pm EST.

sentences.sentence_4: ADDRESSES: The April 14, 2021, meeting will be a virtual meeting.

sentences.sentence_5: FOR FURTHER INFORMATION CONTACT: Heather Harris Pag[aacute]n, ISOO Program Analyst, by telephone at 2023575351, or by email at NISPPAC@naragov SUPPLEMENTARY INFORMATION: This meeting is open to the public in accordance with the Federal Advisory Committee Act (5 USC app 2) and implementing regulations at 41 CFR 101-6.

sentences.sentence_6: The Committee will discuss National Industrial Security Program policy matters.

sentences.sentence_7: Procedures: You must register in advance through the Event Services link [URL] if you wish to attend.

sentences.sentence_8: NISPPAC members, ISOO employees, and speakers should send an email to NISPPAC@naragov for the appropriate registration information instead of registering with the above link.

sentences.sentence_9: Contact us via email at NISPPAC@naragov with any questions.

sentences.sentence_10: Brian P. McLaughlin, Acting Committee Management Officer.
